115
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:03,660
He's just a small-time thug!

116
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,490
He won't pull this off!

117
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:06,580
Only Yu Tiancheng

118
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:07,660
and I can!

119
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:09,730
