Let me tell you,

125
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:21,850
no way!

126
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:24,540
Wan Hai has to be a mobster!

127
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:26,050
If he weren't a mobster,

128
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,930
Yu Tiancheng and I
wouldn't get this mine.

129
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,100
And if I can't have this mine,

130
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,900
