00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,730
we encourage you to settle your disputes
before they escalate.

150
00:08:23,510 --> 00:08:24,610
The reason I came here

151
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:25,900
is to

152
00:08:26,310 --> 00:08:27,250
help settle this issue.

153
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,100
So,

154
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:30,730
Mr. Yu,

155
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,340
you need to give Dacheng Mining

