178
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:13,370
We're here

179
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,490
on behalf of Provincial Procuratorate's

180
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:18,180
Special Task Force
on Wanchuan Mining Accident.

181
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:21,100
