185
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,700
What do you want me to do?

186
00:10:38,390 --> 00:10:39,580
So Wan Hai isn't cooperating, huh?

187
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,820
Have you considered

188
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:44,850
why he isn't cooperating?

189
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:49,130
The legal system

190
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:52,490
is the last line of defense

191
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,580
for social justice.

192
00:10:55,150 --> 00:10:56,460
But if the judiciary

193
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,700
and legal procedures aren't fair,

194
00:10:57,790 --> 00:10:59,490
