of having just laws?

195
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:02,980
If you don't get that,

196
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:03,770
I have nothing to say to you.

197
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,340
There's a protection network

198
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,490
within Dongping's judicial system.

199
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,700
