201
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:20,530
What you call

202
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:21,820
fairness,

203
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:22,890
justice,

204
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:23,940
truth,

205
