from textbooks.

207
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,300
But real life isn't ideal.

208
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:32,730
It's all about survival.

209
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,220
We have to put up with it.

210
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:38,700
We can't defeat them.

211
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:43,060
I didn't mention it,

212
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:49,300
but

213
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:52,770
