just like that.

224
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:15,530
You couldn't before,

225
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:16,820
but you can now?

226
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:20,650
Please have faith in our determination
and strength this time.

227
00:12:20,670 --> 00:12:21,730
