234
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:53,850
right?

235
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:56,770
We set up this special task force

236
00:12:57,790 --> 00:12:58,890
because of that evidence,

237
00:13:00,670 --> 00:13:02,460
that someone caused the mining accident.

238
00:13:06,630 --> 00:13:08,650
