had Wan Chao reach out to me.

241
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,770
It's unclear whether Wan Chao is alive.

242
00:13:18,910 --> 00:13:20,340
We have a moral and legal obligation

243
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:22,420
to thoroughly investigate
the Wan Hai case

244
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,130
and restore the Wans' reputation.

245
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:26,770
I know you want that too.

246
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:30,700
We really need your help.

247
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,370
Please keep faith in the justice system

248
00:13:34,510 --> 00:13:35,340
and yourself.

249
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:37,490
Having faith that lawyers

250
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,980
are essential for building

251
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,460
a rule-of-law society.

252
00:13:53,510 --> 00:13:54,010
Ms. Zheng,

253
00:13:55,510 --> 00:13:56,890
you might be right,

254
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,770
but I'm ready for a different life.

255
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:05,580
I just want to work my nine-to-five job,

256
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,530
earn a steady paycheck

257
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:09,490
and spend all my free time
with my daughter.

258
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,300
Law is no longer a part of my life,

259
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,130
nor do I want it to be.

260
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,100
I have to go to work now.

261
00:14:22,270 --> 00:14:22,700
Goodbye.

262
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:27,700
Ms. Zhang,

263
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:33,530
we'll meet again.

264
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:47,940
Excuse me.

265
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:48,850
Come in.

